quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  22,23,"That God enters those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, treed gardens/paradises, the rivers/waterways run/flow from beneath/below it, they be bejeweled/decorated in it from bracelets from gold, and pearls, and their cover/dress in it (is) silk"
  22,24,"And they were guided to the good/pure from the words/opinion and belief, and they were guided to the praiseworthy`s/commendable`s road/way"
  22,25,"That those who disbelieved and prevent/obstruct from God`s way/path , and the Mosque the Forbidden/Respected/Sacred which We made/put it to/for the people, equal the devoted/dedicated in it, and the apparent (visitor), and who wants/intends in it by deviation/apostasy with injustice/oppression, We make him taste/experience from a painful torture"